<TEXT>
   Premier Andreas Papandreou has publicly
scolded his American-born wife for delaying a meeting to discuss
their divorce plans.
   ``I asked and hoped that the divorce procedure would be set into
motion before Mrs. Papandreou left for the United States, but she
refused,'' the premier said in a statement Friday.
   Margaret Papandreou left for a monthlong trip to the United
