<HEAD>People in the News</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: SUBS Los Angeles-dated 2nd item to CORRECT spelling of Givens
on first reference.</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LOS ANGELES (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Heavyweight boxing champion Mike Tyson says
his divorce from actress Robin Givens is just a signature away.
   ``I've signed the divorce papers. She's on vacation and when she
comes back and signs them, we'll be legally divorced,'' Tyson said
Friday on ``The Arsenio Hall Show,'' a syndicated talk show.
   Financial terms of the possible settlement weren't disclosed.
