<HEAD>Kidnap Gang Releases Six Captives</HEAD>
<DATELINE>ZAMBOANGA CITY, Philippines (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A band of kidnappers on
Saturday released a civic leader, a businesswoman and four
government employees who were held for ransom two months, officials
said.
