of the Philippines, and the four city employees were abducted Dec.
12 as they were returning from an inspection of some projects.
   Rodriguez said authorities expected only five hostages to be
released but when they arrived at the turnover site, they found that
the kidnappers had also released a busineswoman kidnapped Dec. 2.
